ganga/python/Ganga
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- added outputfilenameformat field in the MassStorageFile. 
It will allow the user to configure the path to the output 
on the mass storage, i.e it could be set to /some/path/here/{jid}/{sjid}/{fname}
or /path/to/my/output/{fname}. {jid}, {sjid} and {fname} are 
keyword parameters that will be replaced respectively by job id, 
subjob id and file name. Some of these parameters are mandatory if
the user sets outputfilenameformat to something different from the
default 'None' value - {fname} is always mandatory, {sjid} is
mandatory if the job is split-job.


